vests in high yield credit convertible preferred stocks convertible bonds and corporate bonds the firm makes use of strategies such as short positions long positions convertible  context capital management llc is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor the firm also provides business consulting services to companies on matters such as corporate restructurings capital formation mergers and acquisitions and management and strategic issues it primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles the firm also caters to high net worth individuals it manages separate clientfocused portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it invests in high yield credit convertible preferred stocks convertible bonds and corporate bonds the firm makes use of strategies such as short positions long positions convertible arbitrage capital structure arbitrage catalystevent driven relative value credit opportunity and fundamental overlay it employs a combination of fundamental analysis and technical analysis with a focus on topdown and bottomup stock picking approach to make its investments the firm uses inhouse research to make its investments context capital management llc was founded in  and is based in la jolla california with an additional office in greenwich connecticut detailed description  avenida de la playasuite la jolla ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwcontextfundscom key executives for context capital management llc mr michael stuart rosen cfa cofounder managing member chief executive officer chief compliance officer and cochairman age  mr william david fertig cofounder managing member chief investment officer and cochairman age  mr theodore tu cfa managing director mr michael f mcnulty cfa director of research mr charles carnegie cfa managing partner and portfolio manager compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states